gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 117, Cavaliers 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets win their fifth straight game as they defeated the Cavaliers, 117-103. All five Houston starters were in double-figures as Jalen Green (26 points, 11 rebounds, four assists) and Jabari Smith Jr. (20 points, seven rebounds) totaled 46 points and Fred VanVleet added 13 points and 16 assists. Caris LeVert led the Cavaliers with 21 points and seven assists. The Rockets move to 32-35 as the Cavs go to 42-25.
